Also, I added couple of controlNet templates, this is the best way to control hands and fingers. You can create your own templates, they should work too. I'll made a tutorial someday about how to do it if you don't know)

You can read a manual about how to use it from here.

Enjoy)

Feel free to ask any questions here in comments, or in my discord channel.

Also I am making games with AI arts. They will be free in the future, but if you want to participate in making or have an early access - you can support me on patreon)
